<ul><li>8+ years&rsquo; experience with commercial and/or utility solar project development</li><li>MBA preferred</li><li>Experience in the CAISO and with CEQA permitting</li><li>Specific expertise in one or more of the following areas: permitting, interconnection, and/or real estate</li><li>Track record of independently leading multi-disciplinary teams in closing utility-scale renewable energy projects</li><li>Knowledge of finance and business concepts</li><li>Energetic and aggressive in pursuing opportunities</li><li>Results-oriented with the ability to work independently, with light supervision, in an entrepreneurial environment</li><li>Strong desire to advance the adoption of renewable energies in the global energy mix</li></ul><p style="margin: 0px;">LI-NT*</p>
